      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65B40 4.0L V8. This specimen boasts a factory-spec 6-speed manual transmission and the optional Competition Package (ZCP), providing a 10mm lower ride height and remapped Electronic Damper Control. Recent preventative maintenance includes treated rod bearings and throttle actuator replacements, ensuring the 8,400 RPM redline is explored with confidence. The chassis remains taut with zero subframe fatigue, and the factory Alpine White paint retains its original depth. A true driver\u2019s machine with no mechanical compromises.",
